file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: Beauty-Docusaurus Project
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Beauty-Docusaurus
  termsOfService: "http://beauty-docusaurus.com"
  contact:
    email: "skdusdl8804@gmail.com"
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: "http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html"
servers:
  - url: "http://localhost:5001/api"

tags:
  - name: config
    description: beauty.saurus.config.json file configuration

components:
  schemas:
    Config:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        type:
          type: string
        color:
          type: string
        position:
          type: string
    Navbar:
      type: object
      properties:
        title:
          type: string
        title-margin:
          type: string
        height:
          type: string
        background-color:
          type: string
        position:
          type: string
          enum: [sticky, tranistion]
        logo-image:
          type: string
        logo-alt:
          type: string
        items:
          type: array
          items: object
          properties:
            $ref: "#/components/schemas/NavItem"
paths:
  /navbar:
    post:
      summary: navbar 속성들을 변경합니다.
      tags:
        - navbar
      requestBody:
        description: Navbar setting json
        required: false
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Navbar"
            example:
              title: Beauty-Saurus
              title-margin: 0 0 0 20px
              height: 60px
              background-color: pink
              position: sticky
              logo-image: img/logo.svg
              logo-alt: mysite logo
              items:
                [
                  { name: "Doc1", type: "doc", color: "", position: "left" },
                  { name: "Doc2", type: "doc", color: "", position: "left" },
                ]

      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
        "404":
          description: Fail
